<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ثُمَّ ارْتَقَتْ عَنِ المُوَاءِ فَعَوَتْ وَهَرَّتِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَرَدَّدَتْ فَحِيحَهَا كَحَيَّةٍ بِقَفْرَةِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بَلْ وَاكْتَسَتْ لي مِنْ وَرَاءِ السِّتْرِ جِلْدَ النِّمْرَةِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>كَرَّتْ وَلَكِنْ كَالجَبَانِ قَاعِدَاً وَفَرَّتِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَانْتَفَضَتْ شَوَارِبَاً عَنْ مِثْلِ بَيْتِ الإِبْرَةِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لَمْ أَجْزِهَا بِسَوْءةٍ لأَجْلِ تِلْكَ الثَّوْرَةِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَلاَ غَبِيتُ ضَعْفَهَا وَلاَ نَسِيتُ قُدْرَتي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَلاَ رَأَيْتُ غَيْرَ أُمٍّ بِالصِّغَارِ بَرَّةِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَيَا لَجِدِّ الأُمَّهَاتِ في بِنَاءِ الأُسْرَةِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَلَمْ أَزَلْ حَتىَّ اطْمَأَنَّ جَأْشُهَا وَقَرَّتِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَجِئْتُهَا بِشَرْبَةٍ مِنْ لَبَنٍ وَكِسْرَةِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلَوْ وَجَدْتُ مِصْيَدَاً لَجِئْتُهَا بِفَأْرَةِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَاضْطَجَعَتْ تحْتَ ظِلاَلِ الأَمْنِ وَاسْتَقَرَّتِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَقَرَأَتْ أَوْرَادَهَا وَمَا دَرَتْ مَا قَرَتِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَعَسْعَسَ الصِّغَارُ في ثُدِيِّهَا فَدَرَّتِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>